Finally, a comment on the marginal nature of the interaction:
performing the ultra-violet limit, except for peculiar values of
the coupling constant, all the scattering matrices' components
remain simultaneously finite.

Correlation functions 

The problem at the heart of this paper concerns the computation of
correlation functions of the local fields , present
in the theory.

