the bulk physics, it is worth performing a rotation in the
Minkowsi plane (, ), moving the defect line at
.  In this new picture, the Hilbert space of states is the
same as in the bulk and the effects of impurities are taken into
account by an operator , placed at , which acts on the
bulk states. Therefore,  correlation functions assume the form
